headline: Is Netflix’s Gaming Expansion Signaling Room for Growth in 2025?
summary: Thinking about what to do with Netflix stock right now? You are in good company. Whether you are holding, buying, or just watching from the sidelines, Netflix has kept investors intrigued with its performance and latest news. Over the last week, the stock jumped 5.8%, and it is up an impressive 68.8% over the past year. Year to date, Netflix is up 37.6%, and the long-term three- and five-year moves—430.5% and 129.9% respectively—only reinforce the sense that we are dealing with a powerhouse...
